嚮英國每一日都擔心比人篤灰，呢樣恐懼做為懲罰先係最大懲罰</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n3.<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">97後手足唔會被割</span></span></strong>，首先，佢地可以跟BNO父母及配偶前往英國。第二，對於<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">未受BNO平權保障嘅人佢哋仲有美國既救生艇計劃</span></span></strong>，該計劃估計幾日內亦會通過。"},{"pid":"87f75571780333d46f01fe94e583702d82a7d0ed","tid":2089249,"uid":105924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"319fb145371b950f3332bdcfe536c9f0057830d2","tid":2089249,"uid":228955,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T14:48:54.000Z","msg":"其實同US個碌卡 五年冇乜分別已經唔差"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T18:50:28.000Z","msg":"直頭係抵玩過美國綠卡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d5cfbed2b04c51c412c15eb177679505bb8fec7","tid":2089249,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T20:20:42.000Z","msg":"『薪火post』BNO 續期資訊(88) 睇頂置 HMPO簽收後30個工作天內更新<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fDREsS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fDREsS</a>"}]}